        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Restore Employment in Natural and Environmental Work Conservation Corps Act or the RENEW Conservation Corps Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the Restore Employment in Natural and Environmental Work Conservation Corps program within the Department of the Interior and Department of Agriculture under which participants must implement eligible projects (e.g., planting trees or controlling invasive species).</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
